t-xaq, jun ja te kolb´il mya b´a´n n-ok tka´yin twitz laguna extzen n-ok tka´yin qa ch´ixtoq tkub´ tz´aq
kub´l. Mintiʼ ok tqʼoʼn twitz tiʼj tej tyolin Jack.
